reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 28, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great value for money. I love it
reviews.reviewText: It was easy to put together and looks better than I expected. It's a very good product for a very good price.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 11, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Cute wood table
reviews.reviewText: I love this table. Easy to assemble and has real wood shelves. It’s worth the money. I would give it 5 stars.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 15, 2023
reviews.reviewText: These tables are perfect night stands and I think provide the perfect amount of surface area for a lamp/glasses/phone whatever else you might have. My only "issue" was that one of the legs on the tables had a stripped screw end. So it didn't lock in place, but since the table portions kind of sandwich the legs in place, it isn't a problem once assembled. Plus I gave that table to my partner, so if it falls, it's his problem...

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 29, 2024
reviews.reviewText: It’s a beautiful stand! Super easy to put together. Not as high as I’d like but I think it’s more my bed that sits too high. Still love it.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 27, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Excellent Plant Stand
reviews.reviewText: These are small units, easy to assemble and we use them for plant stands in the sun room. We’ve ordered 2 pairs and very pleased with them.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 20, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars Bottom screw defective
reviews.reviewText: It’s a nice little side table would work great for the space I am needing it for. The only issue I have is that one of the bottom screws is defective and I can not use which makes the table wobbly.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 14, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Good side tables
reviews.reviewText: The media could not be loaded. Amazing for the price. They hold up pretty good, very sturdy and easy to assemble. The color is great, they definitely look more expensive. Pop some coasters in them and they are as cute as can be.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 11, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Very small but just what I wanted!
reviews.reviewText: Very tight space between recliner and sofa so needed a small table and this fits the bill perfectly. It’s more like step stool size. Lol. So the reviews were right on, but I WANTED small so it’s perfect for me! Pressed wood and nothing to write home about. But still cheaper than those sofa arm tables....I can still use my sofa for....well...a sofa!!

This item worked perfectly. Because of the design flexibility of the product, I purchased two of them and was able to combine them into ONE 3-tier unit, as per the picture illustrates. The narrow size works well to fit the allowable space. The wood shelves fit my decor. It’s VERY sturdy.

reviews.reviewTitle: Excellent small table and easy to assemble.
reviews.reviewText: This is a small table that suits my purpose. It's easy to assemble which is a plus.

reviews.reviewTitle: table pour mettre dans un corridor
reviews.reviewText: Cette petite table sert à mettre un mini arbre de Noel dans l'entrée d'un bloc appartement . De cette façon l'arbre est bien à la vue pour les gens, parfait juste la bonne auteur. La planche de bois est de bonne qualité ainsi que les pattes pour des objets pas trop lourd.
Good quality. Don’t need anything to assemble.
Love this table. I needed something smaller to go between two recliners and it for great, looks great and easy to put together.
